  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 3. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed for the primary flow-field quantities; however, three credibility factors are recorded as not-assessed on the basis that they were considered beyond the scope of the current submission cycle. The remaining ten factors are assessed, with achieved levels meeting or approaching required levels. Decision: Accepted.",
