    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/cardiovascular-cfd-lab-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the seven assessed factors with achieved levels at or near required levels, combined with the overall low assurance level designation, provide sufficient credibility for the intended decision at MRL 3. Three factors (numerical solver error, use error, and test samples) were not assessed on the basis that they were considered beyond the scope of the current submission cycle. The team noted these gaps but determined that the remaining evidence base was adequate for the Low assurance level. Accepted with recommendation to complete outstanding factor assessments in the next submission cycle.",
